        {
            "id": 4094649442674342,
            "definition": {
                "type": "note",
                "content": "[Carbon Black Cloud](https://www.broadcom.com/products/carbon-black/threat-prevention/carbon-black-cloud) is a cloud-native endpoint protection platform that provides centralized visibility and control over endpoint activity. It enables threat detection, investigation, and response through continuous monitoring and behavioral analytics, helping security teams improve defenses and respond faster.\n\nThis dashboard provides a high level summary of alerts, endpoint events, authentication events watchlist hits and audit logs.\n\nFor more information, see the [Carbon Black Cloud Integration Documentation](https://docs.datadoghq.com/integrations/carbon_black_cloud/).\n\n**Tips**\n- Use the timeframe selector in the upper-right corner of the dashboard to change the default timeframe.\n- Clone this dashboard to rearrange, modify, and add widgets and visualizations.",
                "background_color": "blue",
                "font_size": "14",
                "text_align": "left",
                "vertical_align": "center",
                "show_tick": true,
                "tick_pos": "50%",
                "tick_edge": "left",
                "has_padding": true
            },
            "layout": {
                "x": 4,
                "y": 0,
                "width": 8,
                "height": 3
            }
        },
